rows.label: qst101103_msg0001
rows.name:
Uh, I, um...
Thank you very much.

rows.label: qst101103_msg0002
rows.name:
I was picking Confusion Ivy and then
I sort of, well...stepped on some
monsters.

rows.label: qst101103_msg0003
rows.name:
Good thing I'd been practicing
all that tree climbing!

rows.label: qst101103_msg0004
rows.name:
My da said what?
Oh! Oh no! I have to hurry up
and collect what I came for!

rows.label: qst101103_msg0005
rows.name:
I think so...just about...
Here I- Owwww!

rows.label: qst101103_msg0006
rows.name: Think I just twisted my ankle...

rows.label: qst101103_msg0007
rows.name:
Man, what do I do...?
Da can't finish his work without
the Confusion Ivy...

rows.label: qst101103_msg0009
rows.name:
We should be fine with, hm...
Seven more bits of Confusion Ivy.

rows.label: qst101103_msg0010
rows.name:
If you look near trees, you'll find it no
time. Ivy grows up trees, y'see!
